The '''mozz box''' was a [[Music/Legends|musical]] instrument developed during the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

Mozz boxes were used for playing the [[Tatooine blues]].<ref name="hutt">{{FFG|story=The Long Arm of the Hutt|book=Star Wars: Edge of the Empire Beginner Game|text=''Star Wars: Edge of the Empire'' Beginner Game}}</ref>

